You should have $GOPATH/bin in $PATH.

Microservices platform sample using Micro:

  go install github.com/micro/micro/v3@latest

Running it:

  micro server
  micro login # user=admin pass=micro

Run the helloworld service:

  micro run github.com/micro/services/helloworld
  micro status
  micro logs helloworld

Interacting with the helloworld service CLI:

  micro helloworld call --name=Jane
  micro helloworld --help

Also possible with HTTP:

  micro helloworld call --name=Jane

Running a local code:

  cd client
  micro run .
  micro logs client








